>
  <!--
    IA KEY BLOCKS (from information-architecture.md — Student Pharmacy near York University):
    1. SegmentPanel / hero — "Pharmacy for York University students at Keele & Finch" headline + transfer CTA
    2. Fast transfers highlight — "Transfer from your home pharmacy in minutes" ServiceCard
    3. Free delivery highlight — no car needed, we deliver to your door
    4. Multilingual service note — TODO: confirm which languages are spoken at the pharmacy with owner
    5. Proximity to campus — "10 minutes from York University" (TODO: verify travel time)
