  <div class="container section">
    <h1>Student Pharmacy near York University — Keele &amp; Finch</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Your prescriptions shouldn't slow you down. Four Winds Roots Pharmacy is right at
      Keele &amp; Finch — close to campus, fast service, and free delivery to your door.
    </p>

    <section aria-labelledby="students-transfers">
      <h2 id="students-transfers">Transfer Your Prescription from Home</h2>
      <p>
        Coming from out of town? Leave your prescription at your home pharmacy and we'll
        handle the transfer — no calls, no hassle on your end. Just fill out our online form
        and we contact your current pharmacy directly. You get on with your day.
      </p>
      <a href="/services/transfers" class="btn btn-transfer">Transfer My Prescription</a>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="students-delivery">
      <h2 id="students-delivery">Free Delivery — No Car Needed</h2>
      <p>
        We deliver prescriptions at no charge across North York. No minimum order, no delivery
        fee. Request delivery when you submit your refill or transfer online.
        <a href="/services/free-delivery">Learn more about free delivery →</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="students-proximity">
      <h2 id="students-proximity">Close to York University — and Getting Closer</h2>
      <p>
        Four Winds Roots Pharmacy is on Keele Street, just south of Finch Avenue West —
        a short ride from York University's Keele campus.
      </p>
      <p>
        The <strong>Finch West LRT (Line 6)</strong> opened on December 7, 2025, running
        18 stops from <strong>Finch West Station at Keele Street</strong> all the way to
        Humber College. If you're coming from the York University area, Finch West Station
        is your connection point — it's right at our doorstep.
      </p>
      <p>
